uk.ac.ebi.mdk.deprecated
Class MIRIAMEntry

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ebi.mdk.deprecated.MIRIAMEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Resource
public class MIRIAMEntry
extends Object
implements Resource

MIRIAMEntry.java – MetabolicDevelopmentKit – Jun 25, 2011 A Miaram Registry entry (http://www.ebi.ac.uk/miriam/main/) that stores various data about base urn/definition/name etc. The main use is in generating URN annotation for identifiers which is of particular use in SBML Resource MetaInfo 

  MIRIAMEntry chebiRDF = MIRIAMResource.CHEBI.getEntry(); // CheMet-IO (atm) 
  chebiRDF.getBaseURN()                                   // urn:miriam:obo.chebi 
  chebiRDF.getURN("CHEBI:15442")                          // urn:miriam:obo.chebi:CHEBI%A315442

Author:
johnmay
